providers.name: Prince George County Meals on Wheels
providers.description: County-operated Meals on Wheels program delivering nutritious meals to eligible homebound residents.
providers.eligibility: Homebound residents of Prince George County, primarily seniors and adults with disabilities.

providers.name: Prince William County Department of Social Services - Child Care Subsidy
providers.description: Administers child care assistance for Prince William County, including the Quantico area.
providers.eligibility: Residents of Prince William County meeting Virginia Child Care Subsidy requirements.
